org.linqs.psl.database.atom

Class PersistedAtomManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.database.atom.AtomManager
      • org.linqs.psl.database.atom.PersistedAtomManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LazyAtomManager

    public class PersistedAtomManager
extends AtomManager
    Implements the AtomManager with a twist: this AtomManager will only return RandomVariableAtoms that were persisted in the Database at instantiation. All other types of Atoms are returned normally. getAtom() is thread-safe.
